{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a mysterious tower in this world that replicates all sorts of objects from other realities, creating an indefinite space full to the brim with monsters, strange creatures, people, and loot. You have found yourself in this reality, and now it\u2019s your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440380/extras/111.gif?t=1734910861\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Entering the tower, you find yourself in fierce battles that require valuable loot items - armor, magic rings, weapons, and much more. These are essential tools for developing your unique builds while clearing the tower's floors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440380/extras/Sets.gif?t=1734910861\" />Defeat enemies and earn gold, which can be spent on new loot items. Continuously manage your loot to become stronger right in the battle by absorbing the mythical power of the items you discard - even if for a mere moment, but with dedication it\u2019s enough to ascend to near godhood and kill whatever twisted creature stands in your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Loot in Megaloot serves dual purposes: it can be equipped to enhance the player\u2019s character or consumed during battle for immediate stat boosts. After clearing each floor, you have the option to dismantle loot for permanent stat gains, adding layers of strategic depth to the gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440380/extras/dismantle_1.gif?t=1734910861\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine loot strategically to craft dominating builds and become the ultimate power hunter. Balance between strengths and weaknesses to maximize your power to the fullest extent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440380/extras/enemies_1.gif?t=1734910861\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">150+ unique loot items with many variations of characteristics that have a synergistic effect to create unique builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">27+ stats like Toxicity, Strength, Wisdom, Faith, Recovery, and more, which can be combined with loot and keystones for a unique strategy and tactics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 characters with their abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple, addictive, and challenging gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High replayability at any time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440380/extras/ezgif-4-3b5f5b897f.gif?t=1734910861\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fren's Silver Border","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440380/a87401dc485ca0f8858f70a846a4a465fd5d3b21.jpg"},{"name":"Fren's Golden Border","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440380/48bd528ec3f654488dc65a6802dc9e8d0845439c.jpg"},{"name":"Fren's Demonic Border","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440380/ba5ad6819f317f30e954ed800bc46142ed91c813.jpg"},{"name":"Fren's Jaden Border","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440380/ca53d5736987b31221cce5c71a6c37af54858b04.jpg"},{"name":"Fren's Frozen Border","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2440380/af124d6af942d9d3048eb97d257f74ee0b82